race.comment: ETCHED IN TIME (2) talented gelding who looks to get the right setup at his third run back. Chased hard from the sticky gate when a respectable fourth over 1400m at Kembla Grange. Proven at the mile and expected to go close. OKAMI STAR (8) up in trip and class when a plugging sixth over 1550m at Canterbury. Has further improvement to come and should be in this for a long way. HELL'S ITCH (4) back in class when a determined winner here last start. Poorly drawn for this and place prospects best. OHTANI (7) won two back at Canberra and was only narrowly beaten last start at this course, class and distance. Finds yet another small field which he can settle back in and not spot the leaders too much of a head start on straightening.
